{
  "stem": "3605.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So the world was just too cruel for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But later on, as they came by, some of the people that ran away came back to that little town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And even that girlfriend, that Hanka, came back looking for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we found each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we again got organized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I joined the movement of the Bricha, which was the Israeli soldiers that were connected with the English Army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This was the Palestinian Jewish soldiers-- not Israeli.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- because at that time, Israel didn't exist yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I remember we were gathering.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "At that time, I was already over 20.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were gathering the young people under 18 to send them with the [NON-ENGLISH] to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then, May and June came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was taking the transport of the [NON-ENGLISH] to Minhen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there, I met a girl from my hometown that I met in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when I showed her my group picture, her sister was there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So she wanted me to cut out the little head from her sister.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I did that for her, because she didn't have any pictures of the relatives, while I could warm my heart with looking at pictures of my father and of my mother.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were tiny, but they still gave me something that I felt that I came from-- not just from stones.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[CRYING] And later on-- [CRYING] --the losses were great.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I was inconsolable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But still, life was going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I was fortunate to hear in Minhen, that my brother is alive in Bergen-Belsen, because that girl that I gave her the picture of the sister was found by her brothers in Minhen.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I met her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And she told me that my brother is alive in Bergen-Belsen-- that he's very, very sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
